{"event_id": "rtevt:taskrun:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32:286f9e4c:5:654e00cd", "task_run_id": "taskrun:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32:286f9e4c", "event_type": "stage_projection_built", "offset": 5, "created_at": 1777681257.1003294, "payload": {"stage_projection": {"snapshot_id": "stageproj:turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32:a415fec99e7b", "task_id": "turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32", "projection_ref": "27dd6d1e80ceeec9", "prompt_manifest_ref": "manifest-27dd6d1e80ceeec9", "soul_runtime_view": {"soul_id": "runtime", "role_type": "operator", "task_mode": "task.capability_execution", "sections": [{"section_id": "task_section", "title": "任务契约", "source_type": "task_contract", "source_id": "turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32", "owner_layer": "task", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "content": "Goal: 结合知识库风险和 PDF 结论，给我一个一句话判断。\nTask definitions: task.capability_execution\nCompletion criteria: Required capability is selected.; Available operation is executed when required inputs are present.; Answer is grounded in the capability result.", "source_refs": ["task-prompt:turn:2bc80a70a5d94a8ab21e9e7fdecc6f44:32:runtime"], "candidate_refs": [], "chars": 243}, {"section_id": "method_section", "title": "方法摘要", "source_type": "skill_runtime_view", "source_id": "task_prompt_contract.method_section", "owner_layer": "skill", "cache_scope": "dynamic", "visible_to_model": true, "content": "- 知识库问答: 面向本地知识库目录的检索和问答能力，适合事实查询、FAQ 解释和基于本地文档的可追溯回答。 Use for local knowledge-base lookup, factual explanation, and questions that should be answered from local materials. Directly answer the user-facing task. Do not describe internal tool calls, routing policy, or protocol.", "source_refs": ["skill.rag-skill"], "candidate_refs": [], "chars": 276}, {"section_id": "projection_section", "title": "投影姿态", "source_type": "projection_requirement", "source_id": "turn:2bc80a70a5d94